contact_name: Eurostat, the statistical office of the European Union
description: This indicator is defined as the percentage share of road in total inland transport, expressed in tonne-kilometre (tkm). It includes transport by road, rail and inland waterways. Rail and inland waterways transport are based on movements on national territory, regardless of the nationality of the vehicle or vessel. Road transport is based on all movements of vehicles registered in the reporting country.
title: Road share of inland freight transport
